## Advanced Topics

Although using the Mesh Paint tool is extremely easy and intuitive, there are some important considerations to think about, particularly in how you want to affect your meshes. 
Mesh Paint can handle painting on individual level-placed instances of meshes and can also be used to paint weight values for multi-texture setups. These topics are all discussed below.

